flowchart TD
  A[Business problem] --> B[Outcome and owner]
  B --> C[Scope and non-scope]
  C --> D[Actors, journeys, and business rules]
  D --> E[Data and integration boundaries]
  E --> F[Functional requirements]
  F --> G[Technical requirements]
  G --> H[Non-functional requirements]
  H --> I[Security, privacy, and compliance constraints]
  I --> J[Acceptance criteria and tests]
  J --> K[Traceability to risks, controls, and roadmap]
  K --> L{Stakeholder validation complete?}
  L -- no --> M[Resolve facts, assumptions, questions, decisions]
  M --> F
  L -- yes --> N[Ready for implementation planning]
